      interpretations, and share personal dream experiences with a growing
      community of dream researchers and enthusiasts.
    </p>

    <p>
      Start by browsing the <a href="/dictionary">dream dictionary</a>,
      using the <a href="/dream-realness">dream analysis tool</a>,
      or <a href="/create-post">sharing your dreams</a> online.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ================= FEATURES ================= -->
